posts.post_title: Ty Cobb 1/1 Highest PSA Graded card from 1920
posts.post_content:
Here is one for sale. Highest graded PSA Cobb card from 1920 and it is less than $400!

[url=http://www.memorylaneinc.com/site/bid/bidplace.asp?itemid=19212]1920 W516-1 #6 Ty Cobb Hand Cut PSA 5 EX[/url]

The one and only Hand Cut TY COBB from 1920. An action representation of the Georgia Peach, this one has been graded EX 5 by PSA. Cut from a strip in the day, this one stands alone at the top of the grading scale. Here is your chance to buy the highest graded specimen of a 90-year old Ty Cobb card. 

[IMG]http://www.memorylaneinc.com/site/images_items/item_19212_1.jpg[/IMG]
